Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹 丹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basquash 你是何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 從剛才就囉囉嗦嗦說個沒完的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我聽清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是丹．JD
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如假包換的Basquasher
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯曼．霍提
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basquash
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音 聽到聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼了 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古老的3種顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到聲音 分享力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個球…是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話能行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 阿蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星間行走之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是石頭的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個石頭是活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Undergrounf那些閃閃發光的傢伙一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡在阿斯達修地下的謎之礦石阿魯迪麥特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其經過提煉之後就是那邊的阿魯迪紐姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過那個石頭的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星間行走者沉睡其中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫醒他們 就必須將聲音傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠讓星間行走者甦醒的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:21:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮歐蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來傳達 傳說之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並非傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們是偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有歌聲 有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日食永存
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露玖 剛剛灌籃假面扔出的球的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭 石頭的聲音 告訴我們歌詞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是奇妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些我搞不懂的事情就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯曼在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露玖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…真是久違了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就去 艾斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.49,0:23:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.46,0:23:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠去月球了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.67,0:23:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此這裡也不像是夢之國
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:24:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的憧憬之地啊
